WEBVTT

00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:04.680
That all you needed
was a phone, a tablet, or a computer,

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:07.000
an internet connection,

00:04:07.800 --> 00:04:09.616
a confident colleague on the ground

00:04:09.640 --> 00:04:11.200
and one magic ingredient:

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:14.880
an augmented reality
collaboration software.

00:04:16.079 --> 00:04:18.815
Using this augmented reality
collaboration software,

00:04:18.839 --> 00:04:21.896
an expert surgeon
can now virtually transport himself

00:04:21.920 --> 00:04:23.696
into any clinical setting

00:04:23.720 --> 00:04:26.776
simply by using his phone
or tablet or computer,

00:04:26.800 --> 00:04:29.656
and he can visually and practically
interact in an operation

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:31.016
from start to finish,